snippet.title: The First Drums of War | July 2023 Test Aftermovie | Scars of Honor
snippet.description:
🤗A big THANK YOU to our lovely community of players for participating in our July 2023 test! 

⚔️You were the first to test combat and the arena PvP modes. Your feedback was invaluable, pointing out bugs and giving ideas on how to improve the game.

👀Wait, what is that? You just stumbled upon this video and you were not part of our last test?! Don't miss the next one or any other news regarding our project, by registering your account at https://beast.ly/i26esKj! 

You can also win a Supporter account from the Daily Dungeon on our BeastBurst App👇
🍎Apple App Store - https://beast.ly/7fZCVjQ
🤖Google Play Store - https://beast.ly/Nnz53Bu

Scars of Honor is the upcoming, brand-new, free-to-play, no-pay-to-win MMORPG.
Join the development and work side-by-side with the developers, to create the best possible game!
100% community-driven development now is the time to make your wishes come true!

■ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ScarsOfHonor.Official
■ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/scars.of.honor/
■ Twitter: https://twitter.com/scars_of_honor/
■ Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ScarsofHonor/
■ Discord: https://discord.gg/8QqTndQbuG
